title: Bigfoot Series 36 in. Telescoping Car Trunk Shovel with Aluminum Handle
description: The Bigfoot Car Trunk Shovel is a handy tool to keep in your car year round for when Winter throw's you a curve ball. The telescoping handle extends up to 36 in. and collapses to 28 in. for compact car storage. This is the perfect tool to dig your car out of an unexpected snow drift and not let winter slow you down.
